  <brief_title>Effectiveness of MICARDIS® (Telmisartan) on Blood Pressure Control and Quality of Live in Patients With Essential Hypertension</brief_title>
  <acronym>MicCAT</acronym>
  <official_title>An Open-label Evaluation of the Effectiveness of MICARDIS® (Telmisartan) on Blood Pressure Control and Quality of Life in Patients With Essential Hypertension The MICARDIS COMMUNITY ACCESS TRIAL (MicCAT)</official_title>
